				<baseName xml:lang="zh">风轮机转子的变桨轴承</baseName>
			</name>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="en">Blade bearing</common:synonyms>
			<common:synonyms xml:lang="zh">Blade bearing</common:synonyms>
			<classificationInformation>
				<common:classification name="ILCD 1.1" classes="../ILCDClassification.xml">
					<common:class level="0">Systems</common:class>
					<common:class level="1">Other machines</common:class>
				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">The pitch bearing, also known as blade bearing, is a component of modern wind turbines which connect the rotor hub and the rotor blade. It allows the required oscillation to control the loads and power of the wind turbine. In wind energy, a pitch bearing is used to change the alignment of a rotor blade about its longitudinal axis. It is subject to considerable static and dynamic forces.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">变桨轴承又称叶片轴承，是现代风力发电机的一个部件，连接转子轮毂和转子叶片。它可以实现所需的摆动，以控制风力涡轮机的负载和功率。在风能领域，变桨轴承用于改变转子叶片围绕其纵轴的排列。它受到相当大的静态和动态力的作用。</common:generalComment>
